window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When <i>Harry Met Sally</i> meets <i>One Day</i>, <i>The Five-Year Hitch</i> is the story of two friends who have known each other all their lives - falling in and out of love. Sam and Miles belong together, except every five years, there’s a hitch and they don’t end up together. Now, as they tell their story to a reporter at a momentous occasion, will they finally break the five-year curse? Can these two friends and lovers find their happily ever after?</p> <p>This title contains adult language. Listener discretion is advised. </p>"; 
